<h2>Geographic Location</h2>

<p>
Riverbend lies along a wide bend in the Silver River,
approximately 120 km inland from the coast.
The surrounding region consists of rolling hills and fertile farmland.
</p>

<h2>Climate</h2>

<p>
Riverbend has a humid temperate climate with warm summers and cool winters.
The nearby river moderates temperatures and produces frequent fog in autumn.
</p>

<ul>
<li>Average summer temperature: 27°C</li>
<li>Average winter temperature: 4°C</li>
<li>Annual rainfall: 900 mm</li>
</ul>

